Spinopelvic fusion surgery from lower thoracic spine to pelvis increased hip 
joint moment-motion analysis.

Kozaki T(1), Hashizume H(2), Oka H(3), Katsuhira J(4), Kawabata K(5), Takashi 
M(6), Iwasaki H(2), Tsutsui S(2), Takami M(2), Nagata K(2), Ishimoto Y(2), 
