Kiwi Fruits Preservation Using Novel Edible Active Coatings Based on Rich Thymol 
Halloysite Nanostructures and Chitosan/Polyvinyl Alcohol Gels.

Salmas CE(1), Giannakas AE(2), Moschovas D(1), Kollia E(3), Georgopoulos S(2), 
