Effects of the Practice of Movement Representation Techniques in People 
Undergoing Knee and Hip Arthroplasty: A Systematic Review.

Riquelme-Hernández C(1), Reyes-Barría JP(2)(3), Vargas A(3), Gonzalez-Robaina 
Y(4), Zapata-Lamana R(4), Toloza-Ramirez D(5)(6), Parra-Rizo MA(7)(8), Cigarroa 
